# GitHub PR Links

This repo lives at https://github.com/zdt90/opcode (a personal fork).

When providing a PR link, always use the GitHub compare URL that targets `zdt90/opcode:main` as the base:

```
https://github.com/zdt90/opcode/compare/main...zdt90:opcode:<branch-name>
```

Never use the `/pull/new/<branch>` form — it requires manual base selection.

# PR Content Language

PR titles, descriptions, and body text (Summary / Changes / Test plan, etc.)
must always be written in English, regardless of the language used in the chat.
